  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Esso Community Sport for Change Project - Research &amp; Consultation</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project gathers factual evidence that shapes future work in Arusha, Tanzania&#x2019;s second largest city. It is designed to engage the most vulnerable and disadvantaged young people, aged between 15 and 24 years, who live in a slum community. The research evaluates how sports activities can be used as a vehicle through which these young people can receive support, enabling them to gain access to housing, health and educational services.</narrative>
  </description>
